 <chapter>
   <title>Acceptance Test Plan Format</title>
     <para>The following table will be used for the acceptance test
plan. This table will list all of the expected goals of each function
described in section 3.1 of the Requirements Specification. For each
goal, the required inputs and the expected output will be listed.
These goals we be used to test the VVS. These tests will ensure that
the product Vorpal Longsword +1 is building is the exact product
Morgantown University is requisitioning.
     </para>
